caption: Presenting “LUNCH AT TWO FOR THREE” my latest fine art limited edition release. No need to ask, he’s a smooth operator, guiding his ladies across Lake Como to the exclusive @villadestelakecomo , the only way he knows. With two aboard and one in tow this is no place for beginners or sensitive hearts. His iconic Aquarama effortlessly cuts the lake in two, as the three arrive just in time for a pre-lunch glass of Bollinger. This new piece breaks waves redefining luxury in @rivayacht speedboats, sharp blazers and high speed dining!
